BEST FRIEND TECH said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 1.52% to NT$85,408,000 from NT$86,727,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales             85,408           86,727    
YOY%              -1.52%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            262,320          288,201    
YOY%              -8.98% 
=================================================================
 